20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBairwa%20belongs%20to%20a%20Dalit%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20month%20later%2C%20Bairwa%20has%20been%20suspended%20by%20the%20state%20education%20department%20on%20the%20instructions%20of%20minister%20Madan%20Dilawar%2C%20and%20asked%20to%20report%20to%20duty%20in%20Bikaner%2C%20more%20than%20600%20kms%20from%20her%20home.%20The%20suspension%20of%20Bairwa%20has%20led%20to%20state-wide%20protests%20by%20Dalit%20groups%2C%20who%20are%20demanding%20the%20revocation%20of%20Bairwa%E2%80%99s%20suspension%20and%20resignation%20of%20the%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%20from%20January%2026%20this%20year%2C%20Bairwa%20can%20be%20seen%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20garlanded%20photos%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20Savitribai%20Phule%20and%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20while%20a%20group%20of%20men%20are%20confronting%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EBacchon%20ki%20devi%20to%3C%2Fem%3E%20Saraswati%20%3Cem%3Ehai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(the%20goddess%20of%20children%20is%20Saraswati)%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20men%20are%20heard%20saying%2C%20to%20which%20Bairwa%20replies%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EBacchon%20ki%20devi%20toh%3C%2Fem%3E%20Savitribai%20Phule%20%3Cem%3Ehai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(the%20goddess%20of%20children%20is%20Savitribai%20Phule).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20men%20insist%20that%20Bairwa%20do%20a%20puja%20of%20the%20Hindu%20deity%20Saraswati%2C%20she%20is%20seen%20refusing.%20Thereafter%2C%20the%20men%20assembled%20in%20front%20of%20the%20school%20are%20seen%20challenging%20her%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20the%20programme.%20One%20of%20the%20men%20asks%20why%20there%20was%20no%20lamp%20and%20whether%20Bairwa%20is%20ignorant%20of%20Hindu%20traditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20the%20meaning%20of%20Hindu%3F%20Hindu%2C%20Muslim%2C%20Sikh%2C%20Isai%3Cem%3E%20sab%20barabar%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Hindu%2C%20Muslim%2C%20Sikh%2C%20Christian%20are%20all%20equal)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bairwa%20is%20heard%20saying%20in%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fkota-three-muslim-govt-school-teachers-suspended-over-forced-religious-conversion-of-students%5C%22%3EKota%3A%20Three%20Muslim%20Govt%20School%20Teachers%20Suspended%20Over%20%E2%80%98Forced%20Religious%20Conversion%E2%80%99%20of%20Students%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETwo%20FIRs%20lodged%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20incident%2C%20two%20FIRs%20%E2%80%93%20one%20by%20Bairwa%20against%20the%20men%20who%20had%20confronted%20her%20and%20the%20other%20against%20her%20for%20hurting%20religious%20sentiments%20%E2%80%93%20were%20registered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20Republic%20Day%2C%2026%20January%202024%2C%20while%20discharging%20my%20duties%20as%20a%20government%20servant%2C%20I%20was%20working%20in%20the%20school%20to%20celebrate%20the%2075th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20sacred%20Constitution%20of%20India.%20Hansraj%20Nagar%2C%20Radheshyam%20Nagar%2C%20Bharat%20Nagar%2C%20Kishan%20Nagar%20and%20other%20members%20of%20a%20same%20family%20of%20the%20village%20and%20teachers%20Hansraj%20Sain%20and%20Bhupendra%20Sain%20of%20the%20school%20staff%20started%20harassing%20me%20for%20Saraswati%20Puja%20in%20a%20public%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20FIR%20registered%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20Bairwa%E2%80%99s%20complaint%20at%20the%20Nahargarh%20police%20station%20in%20Baran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20female%20public%20servant%20from%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20(SC)%20category.%20Hansraj%20Nagar%2C%20Bharat%20Nagar%2C%20Radheshyam%20Nagar%20used%20casteist%20slurs%20and%20said%20that%20we%20will%20see%20you%20outside%E2%80%A6I%20have%20been%20feeling%20mentally%20scared%20since%20this%20incident%20disrupted%20the%20celebration%20of%20the%20national%20festival%20Republic%20Day%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20FIR.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20lodged%20by%20Bairwa%20adds%20that%20there%20is%20no%20mention%20of%20Saraswati%20Puja%20in%20Article%2028%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAccording%20to%20the%20Indian%20Constitution.%2051(a)%20Imaginary%20things%20are%20prohibited%20from%20the%20scientific%20point%20of%20view%E2%80%A6.my%20fundamental%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20expression%20has%20been%20publicly%20violated%E2%80%A6The%20dignity%20of%20women%20has%20been%20violated.%20I%20demand%20strict%20action%20against%20anti-social%20elements%2C%20unconstitutional%20elements%2C%20anti-constitutional%20elements%2C%20elements%20against%20the%20father%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%20Dr.%20Bhimrao%20Ambedkar.%20The%20applicants%20are%20feeling%20unsafe%20after%20this%20incident%2C%E2%80%9D%20reads%20the%20FIR%20lodged%20by%20Bairwa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%20registered%20by%20Bairwa%20belong%20to%20various%20OBC%20caste%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20lodged%20by%20Bairwa%20has%20been%20registered%20under%20sections%20506%20(punishment%20for%20criminal%20intimidation)%20and%20504%20(Intentional%20insult%20with%20intent%20to%20provoke%20breach%20of%20the%20peace)%20of%20the%20IPC%20along%20with%20relevant%20provisions%20of%20the%20SC%2FST%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20and%20Circle%20Officer%20(CO)%2C%20Shahbad%2C%20Baran%2C%20Hemant%20Gautam%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20an%20FIR%20was%20also%20registered%20against%20Bairwa%20by%20locals%20in%20which%20she%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20hurting%20religious%20sentiments%20by%20her%20opinion%20on%20goddess%20Saraswati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20FIR%20against%20government%20teacher%20Hemlata%20Bairwa%20has%20been%20lodged%20by%20locals%20under%20sections%20including%20sections%20153A%20(Promoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20groups%20on%20grounds%20of%20religion%2C%20race%2C%20place%20of%20birth%2C%20residence)%20and%20295A%20(Deliberate%20and%20malicious%20acts%2C%20intended%20to%20outrage%20religious%20feelings%20of%20any%20class%20by%20insulting%20its%20religion%20or%20religious%20beliefs)%20of%20the%20IPC.%20They%20have%20accused%20her%20of%20hurting%20religious%20sentiments.%20Investigation%20is%20being%20conducted%20for%20the%20FIR%20registered%20by%20Bairwa%20and%20also%20the%20one%20registered%20against%20her.%20No%20arrests%20have%20been%20made%20so%20far%20in%20either%20of%20the%C2%A0FIRs%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20CO%20Gautam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESuspension%20after%20education%20minister%E2%80%99s%20public%20declaration%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20January%2026%20incident%2C%20senior%20BJP%20MLA%20and%20Rajasthan%20Education%20Minister%20Madan%20Dilawarhad%20had%20said%20that%20an%20inquiry%20will%20be%20conducted%20into%20the%20incident.%20Bairwa%20was%20suspended%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20have%20got%20so%20pricey%20that%20even%20now%20they%20have%20not%20changed%20their%20ways%2C%20they%20say%20what%20role%20does%20Saraswati%20ma%20have%20in%20school.%20The%20person%20who%20has%20said%20this%20in%20this%20region%2C%20I%20suspend%20that%20person%20and%20make%20Bikaner%20that%20person%E2%80%99s%20office.%20I%20have%20given%20instructions%20to%20officials%20one%20hour%20back%20to%20suspend%20that%20person%20and%20make%20Bikaner%20the%20headquarters%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dilawar%20had%20said%20in%20a%20public%20meeting%20in%20Baran%20last%20week%20as%20the%20people%20assembled%20at%20the%20event%20hailed%20the%20decision%20with%20chants%20of%20Bharat%20Mata%20ki%20Jai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESixty-four-year-old%20Dilawar%2C%20who%20has%20been%20given%20the%20important%20portfolio%20of%20school%20education%20in%20the%20Bhajan%20Lal%20Sharma-led%20BJP%20government%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20himself%20belongs%20to%20the%20Dalit%20community%20and%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20firebrand%20Hindutva%20faces%20of%20the%20saffron%20party%20in%20the%20state.%20He%20is%20often%20in%20the%20news%20for%20his%20statements.%20Ever%20since%20he%20has%20taken%20charge%20as%20education%20minister%2C%20he%20has%20been%20grabbing%20headlines%20for%20reasons%20such%20as%20his%20insistence%20on%20Surya%20Namaskar%20during%20morning%20assembly%2C%20calling%20Mughal%20emperor%20Akbar%20a%20%E2%80%98rapist%E2%80%99%20and%20with%20his%20statements%20against%20wearing%20Hijab%20in%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2023%2C%20the%20office%20of%20the%20District%20Education%20Officer%20(headquarters)%2C%20Elementary%2C%20Baran%20issued%20an%20order%2C%20which%20said%20that%20it%20has%20been%20decided%20to%20initiate%20disciplinary%20action%20against%20Bairwa%20and%20she%20is%20being%20suspended%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%20with%20her%20headquarters%20being%20changed%20to%20Bikaner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98I%20am%20being%20targeted%20because%20of%20my%20caste%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Bairwa%20said%20that%20she%20is%20being%20harassed%20only%20because%20of%20her%20caste%20and%20that%20she%20will%20not%20be%20going%20to%20Bikaner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20Republic%20Day%20and%20I%20was%20doing%20my%20duty%20as%20per%20the%20constitution.%20At%20first%20two%20teachers%20of%20the%20school%2C%20Hansraj%20Sain%20and%20Bhupendra%20Sain%20pressurised%20me%20to%20worship%20Saraswati.%20Then%20they%20left%20and%20returned%20later%20with%20more%20villagers%20who%20started%20harassing%20me.%20They%20abused%20me%20with%20casteist%20slurs.%20Now%2C%20I%20have%20been%20suspended%20and%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20report%20at%20Bikaner%2C%20which%20is%20600%20kms%20away%20from%20my%20home.%20I%20have%20decided%20not%20to%20go%20there%20as%20I%20cannot%20accept%20this%20injustice.%20I%20am%20being%20harassed%20only%20because%20of%20a%20casteist%20mindset%20as%20I%20am%20from%20the%20scheduled%20caste%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bairwa%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBairwa%20also%20slammed%20minister%20Dilawar%20for%20announcing%20her%20suspension%20at%20the%20public%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20is%20it%20fine%20to%20threaten%20me%20on%20a%20public%20stage%3F%20I%20filed%20an%20FIR%20and%20yet%2C%20no%20arrests%20have%20been%20made%20till%20now.%20Instead%2C%20I%20have%20been%20suspended.%20Some%20of%20the%20accused%20regularly%20display%20casteism%20at%20the%20school%20where%20Dalit%20children%20face%20harassment%2C%E2%80%9D%20alleged%20Bairwa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSavitribhai%20Phule%20opened%20schools%20for%20women.%20How%20many%20women%20were%20literate%20before%20her%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBairwa%20stood%20by%20her%20actions%2C%20and%20said%20that%20religious%20beliefs%20are%20personal%20and%20she%20only%20followed%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CReligious%20beliefs%20are%20personal.%20Be%20it%20the%20Constitution%20or%20a%20place%20such%20as%20schools%2C%20religious%20beliefs%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20here.%20How%20can%20the%20minister%20deliver%20a%20speech%20from%20a%20public%20stage%20saying%20that%20he%20is%20suspending%20me%3F%20This%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20respect.%20Are%20we%20his%20servants%20that%20he%20can%20announce%20our%20suspension%20from%20any%20place%3F%20I%20have%20done%20my%20work%20within%20the%20ambit%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20I%20want%20justice%20and%20action%20against%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDalit%20groups%20protest%2C%20lock%20school%2C%20allege%20police%20action%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20Bairwa%E2%80%99s%20suspension%2C%20Dalit%20groups%20across%20the%20state%20have%20been%20agitating%2C%20demanding%20that%20the%20decision%20be%20revoked.%20Members%20of%20Dalit%20outfits%20also%20held%20a%20dharna%20in%20front%20of%20the%20government%20upper%20primary%20school%2C%20Lakdai%20in%20Baran%20district%2C%20where%20Bairwa%20was%20posted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDalit%20groups%20alleged%20that%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20February%2027%2C%20that%20some%20protesters%20were%20injured%20after%20police%20allegedly%20used%20force%20on%20agitators%20sitting%20on%20dharna%20in%20front%20of%20the%20school.%20The%20Baran%20police%20denied%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20Rajasthan%20police%20destroyed%20the%20peaceful%20protest%20in%20support%20of%20Hemlata%20Bairwa.%20Hemlata%20was%20fired%20from%20her%20job%20by%20the%20Education%20Minister%20a%20few%20days%20ago.%20She%20had%20asked%20what%20was%20the%20contribution%20of%20Saraswati%20Devi%20in%20education%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fawz1obeRfP%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fawz1obeRfP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20The%20Dalit%20Voice%20(%40ambedkariteIND)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FambedkariteIND%2Fstatus%2F1762475055295176753%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2027%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSchoolchildren%20and%20Bhim%20Army%20members%20had%20locked%20the%20school%20gates%20and%20sat%20on%20dharna.%20Police%20beat%20the%20protesters%20with%20lathis%20which%20resulted%20in%20injuries%20to%20some%20of%20the%20agitators.%20We%20stand%20with%20Hemlata%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Till%20the%20time%20her%20suspension%20is%20not%20revoked%2C%20we%20will%20hold%20more%20protests.%20Ever%20since%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20come%20to%20power%2C%20officials%20from%20the%20SC%20and%20minority%20communities%20are%20being%20targeted.%20Education%20minister%20Madan%20Dilawar%2C%20who%20himself%20belongs%20to%20a%20Dalit%20community%2C%20has%20been%20given%20the%20ministerial%20post%20to%20target%20his%20own%20people%E2%80%A6We%20demand%20that%20Dilawar%20be%20removed%20from%20his%20ministerial%20post%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Anil%20Dhenwal%2C%20Rajasthan%20in-charge%20of%20the%20Bhim%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Baran%20police%20denied%20the%20allegations%20of%20lathi%20charge%20and%20said%20that%20the%20protesters%20were%20dispersed%20from%20the%20dharna%20site%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20avoid%20a%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20and%20the%20school%20was%20reopened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20exactly%20lathi%20charge%20that%20has%20taken%20place.%20Certain%20people%20had%20locked%20the%20door%20of%20the%20school%20and%20they%20were%20agitating%20over%20why%20the%20teacher%20Hemlata%20Bairwa%20was%20suspended%20and%20her%20headquarter%20changed%20to%20Bikaner.%20But%20their%20procedure%20of%20protesting%20was%20against%20law.%20They%20also%20misguided%20some%20students%20who%20said%20that%20the%20school%20should%20not%20be%20opened.%20Later%2C%20another%20group%2C%20who%20were%20in%20favour%20of%20opening%20the%20school%20also%20reached%20the%20site.%20They%20said%20either%20police%20should%20open%20the%20school%20or%20they%20themselves%20would.%20It%20resulted%20in%20a%20tussle%20between%20the%20two%20groups%20and%20a%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20was%20about%20to%20arise%20as%20the%20two%20groups%20were%20about%20to%20fight%2C%E2%80%9D%20Baran%20SP%20Raj%20Kumar%20Chaudhary%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaudhary%20added%20that%20after%20trying%20to%20convince%20the%20two%20groups%2C%20the%20police%20had%20to%20intervene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDalit%20rights%20activists%20say%20that%20the%20suspension%20of%20Bairwa%20has%20been%20done%20with%20malice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20suspend%20Hemlata%20Bairwa%20and%20to%20change%20her%20headquarters%20to%20Bikaner%20is%20unjust.%20The%20education%20minister%2C%20instead%20of%20answering%20her%20question%20about%20what%20contribution%20Saraswati%20had%20in%20education%2C%20took%20this%20action.%20If%20they%20felt%20bad%2C%20or%20took%20it%20as%20a%20challenge%2C%20they%20should%20have%20countered%20it%20by%20answering%20and%20not%20by%20taking%20action.%20Hemlata%20didn%E2%80%99t%20say%20anything%20wrong%20as%20even%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20who%20belongs%20to%20the%20same%20party%20as%20the%20education%20minister%2C%20too%20pays%20his%20tribute%20to%20Savitribai%20Phule%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bhanwar%20Meghwanshi%2C%20Rajasthan%20president%20of%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Union%20for%20Civil%20Liberties%20(PUCL).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%88%20%E0%A4%AB%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AE%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%89%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%A4%20%E0%A4%89%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%95%20%E0%A4%8F%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%BE%2C%20%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%94%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A3%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%8F%20%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A4%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BE%E0%A5%A4%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%95%20%E0%A4%9A%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%8F%20%E0%A4%89%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%98%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B7%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4