Crisis%20Deepens%2C%20Virbhadra%20Singh's%20Son%20Quits%20As%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECompounding%20the%20Congress's%20problems%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20state%20minister%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%20quit%20as%20minister%20this%20morning%20after%20accusing%20Chief%20Minister%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%20of%20overlooking%20MLAs%20and%20disrespecting%20his%20father%20and%20Congress's%20tallest%20leader%20in%20the%20hill%20state%2C%20the%20late%20Virbhadra%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20amid%20dramatic%20developments%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20over%20the%20past%2024%20hours%20that%20turned%20an%20election%20for%20a%20single%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat%20to%20the%20Congress%20government's%20fight%20for%20survival.%20The%20party%2C%20which%20has%2040%20MLAs%20in%20the%2068-member%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20media%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20the%20developments%20in%20the%20hill%20state%20are%20a%20cause%20for%20concern.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20go%20into%20the%20background%20and%20see%20what%20led%20to%20this%20situation.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20rewind%20your%20memory.%20The%202022%20Assembly%20elections%20were%20found%20and%20won%20under%20the%20collective%20leadership%20of%20then%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20Mukesh%20Agnihotri%2C%20state%20Congress%20chief%20Pratibha%20Singh%20and%20campaign%20committee%20head%20and%20current%20Chief%20Minister%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu.%20There%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20polls%20were%20fought%20in%20the%20name%20of%20former%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20late%20Virbhadra%20Singh.%20There%20was%20no%20banner%20or%20poster%20that%20did%20not%20have%20his%20photo.%20A%20day%20before%20the%20polls%2C%20a%20full-page%20newspaper%20ad%20had%20his%20photo%20with%20the%20message%2C%20'Remember%20me%2C%20vote%20in%20my%20name'.%20This%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20record%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20then%20state%20Congress%20chief%20and%20Mr%20Singh's%20mother%20Pratibha%20was%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20frontrunner%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post%20before%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20chose%20Mr%20Sukhu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20past%20one%20year%2C%20I%20have%20not%20said%20a%20word%20on%20the%20government's%20functioning.%20But%20it%20is%20my%20responsibility%20to%20the%20people%20to%20speak%20out%20now.%20The%20post%20is%20not%20important%20for%20me.%20What%20is%20important%20is%20my%20relationship%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20relationship%20of%20trust%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20the%20government%20has%20functioned%2C%20the%20negligence%20towards%20MLAs%2C%20the%20drowning%20of%20their%20voices%20has%20led%20us%20to%20this%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20targeted%20the%20Congress%20government%20over%20its%20functioning%20and%20fiscal%20mismanagement.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20repeatedly%20raised%20with%20the%20party%20high%20command%2C%20but%20they%20did%20not%20react%20the%20way%20they%20should%20have.%20I%20have%20always%20behaved%20in%20calling%20a%20spade%20a%20spade.%20We%20raised%20it%20on%20multiple%20forums%2C%20but%20since%20I%20am%20a%20disciplined%20member%20of%20the%20party%2C%20I%20know%20where%20to%20draw%20the%20line%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20said%20the%20youth%20of%20the%20state%20backed%20the%20Congress.%20%26quot%3BBut%20are%20we%20in%20a%20position%20to%20fulfil%20the%20promises%20to%20the%20youth%20of%20the%20state%3F%20That%20is%20a%20question%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20thought%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20government%2C%20which%20held%20a%20comfortable%20majority%20till%20yesterday%2C%20faces%20a%20crisis%20after%20six%20of%20its%20MLAs%20cross-voted%20in%20the%20contest%20for%20the%20lone%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat%20yesterday.%20The%20rebel%20MLAs%20were%20whisked%20away%20to%20Haryana%20yesterday%2C%20and%20the%20Opposition%20BJP%20today%20claimed%20that%20the%20ruling%20party%20had%20lost%20the%20mandate%20to%20continue%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cross-voting%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20the%20victory%20of%20BJP's%20Harsh%20Mahajan%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election%20after%20a%20tie%2C%20and%20then%20a%20draw%20of%20lots%2C%20sealed%20the%20fate%20of%20Congress%20pick%20and%20senior%20lawyer%20Abhishek%20Singhvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709100600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fpbcmfuac_vikramaditya-singh-facebook_625x300_30_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-leader-virbhadra-singhs-son-vikramaditya-singh-resigns-as-himachal-minister-5141902%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Compounding%20the%20Congress's%20problems%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20state%20minister%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%20quit%20as%20minister%20this%20morning%20after%20accusing%20Chief%20Minister%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%20of%20overlooking%20MLAs%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-leader-virbhadra-singhs-son-vikramaditya-singh-resigns-as-himachal-minister-5141902%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-leader-virbhadra-singhs-son-vikramaditya-singh-resigns-as-himachal-minister-5141902%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-leader-virbhadra-singhs-son-vikramaditya-singh-resigns-as-himachal-minister-5141902%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sri%20Lanka%20'white%20party'%20cancelled%20after%20backlash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709100341000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F1146D%2Fproduction%2F_132756707_gettyimages-1239653630.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68421131