20withheld%20since%20the%20night%20of%20the%20protest%20on%20February%2015%2C%202024%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fnorth-east%2Fmanipur-tribal-body-claims-relief-withheld-in-kuki-zo-majority-churachandpur-district%2Fcid%2F2003430%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20claimed%20that%20deputy%20commissioner%20(DC)%20%E2%80%9Crefused%E2%80%9D%20to%20release%20rations%20for%20the%20past%20two%20weeks%2C%20putting%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20than%2017%2C000%20IDPs%20at%20the%20risk%20of%20starvation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20another%20form%20of%20discrimination%2C%20whereby%20the%20DC%20is%20punishing%20people%20who%20have%20already%20lost%20their%20homes%20by%20threatening%20to%20starve%20them.%20We%20request%20the%20central%20government%20to%20urgently%20intervene%20so%20that%20the%20supply%20of%20rations%20to%20relief%20centres%20is%20resumed%20at%20the%20earliest%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ITLF%20has%20claimed%20in%20the%20memorandum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ITLF%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20came%20two%20days%20after%20the%20Manipur%20government%20dismissed%20reports%20that%20emerged%20out%20of%20Churachandpur%20that%20the%20district%20authorities%20were%20delaying%20the%20release%20of%20ration%20after%20the%20February%2015%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2015%2C%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20Churachandpur%20town%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20suspension%20of%20a%20constable%20by%20the%20superintendent%20of%20police%20(SP)%2C%20leading%20to%20attacks%20on%20the%20SP%E2%80%99s%20and%20DC%E2%80%99s%20offices%20and%20the%20DC%E2%80%99s%20residence%20and%20resulting%20in%20the%20death%20of%20two%20persons%20in%20firing%20by%20security%20personnel.%20The%20government%20in%20response%20banned%20the%20internet%20in%20the%20district%20until%20March%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Manipur%20home%20department%20said%20that%20the%20Churachandpur%20DC%20%E2%80%9Chas%20always%20ensured%20that%20all%20relief%20materials%20such%20as%20rice%2C%20dal%2C%20vegetables%20and%20other%20consumables%20are%20released%20in%20a%20timely%20manner%E2%80%9D%20through%20local%20civil%20society%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20also%20went%20on%20to%20claim%20that%20the%20relief%20was%20last%20distributed%20on%20February%2012-13%20when%20%E2%80%9Cabout%2050%2C000kg%20of%20rice%2C%20245%20bags%20of%20dal%2C%2055%20bags%20of%20sugar%20and%20other%20consumables%20such%20as%20vegetables%2C%20cooking%20oil%2C%20eggs%2C%20tea%20leaf%20and%20spices%20were%20released%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20also%20claimed%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20official%20documents%20and%20records%20were%20burnt%20in%20the%20February%2015%20arson%20and%20that%20two%20of%20the%2012%20vehicles%20damaged%20that%20night%20were%20used%20for%20distribution%20of%20relief%20materials%20in%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20an%20additional%20superintendent%20of%20police%2C%20posted%20in%20the%20operations%20wing%20of%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20at%20Wangkhei%20in%20Imphal%20East%20district%2C%20was%20abducted%20by%20armed%20men%20and%20was%20later%20rescued%20after%20swift%20action%20by%20police%20and%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20ethnic%20conflict%20between%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20communities%20since%20May%203%20has%20left%20at%20least%20213%20dead%20and%20over%2067%2C000%20displaced%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20situation%20remains%20tense%20and%20is%20set%20to%20dominate%20the%20Assembly%20session%20starting%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709098798000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22095913%2FF6ga_ibawAAlDWp.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-relief-material-being-withheld-in-tribal-majority-churachandpur-alleges-kuki-zo-outfit%22%2