c%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbiden-hints-at-truce-in-gaza-during-ramadan-if-hostages-released%2Famp_articleshow%2F108060176.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbiden-hints-at-truce-in-gaza-during-ramadan-if-hostages-released%2Famp_articleshow%2F108060176.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Day%20After%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Stunner%2C%20BJP%20Seeks%20No-Trust%20Vote%20In%20Himachal%20Pradesh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20and%20other%20BJP%20MLAs%20this%20morning%20met%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20Governor%2C%20seeking%20a%20test%20of%20strength%20for%20the%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu-led%20government%20in%20the%20state%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20a%20day%20after%20the%20BJP%20managed%20to%20pull%20off%20a%20victory%20for%20its%20candidate%20in%20the%20lone%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat.%20The%20BJP's%20win%20was%20the%20result%20of%20cross-voting%20by%20Congress%20MLAs%20and%20a%20draw%20of%20lots%20that%20went%20in%20its%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20pulled%20off%20a%20victory%20when%20our%20chances%20seemed%20very%20low.%20BJP%20candidate%20Harsh%20Mahajan%20won%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections.%20Currently%2C%20the%20Congress%20government%20has%20lost%20the%20moral%20right%20to%20stay%20in%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Jairam%20Thakur%20said%20after%20meeting%20the%20Governor%20Shiv%20Pratap%20Shukla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJairam%20Thakur%20alleged%20that%20the%20marshals%20misbehaved%20and%20manhandled%20BJP%20members%20when%20they%20wanted%20to%20speak%20to%20Speaker%20Kuldeep%20Singh%20Pathania%20after%20he%20did%20not%20allow%20division%20of%20votes%20in%20cut%20motions%20pertaining%20to%20the%20health%20department.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20apprised%20the%20Governor%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20comes%20amid%20a%20buzz%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20move%20a%20