tate%20for%20damage%20control.%20The%20BJP%2C%20a%20fast%20mover%20in%20these%20situations%2C%20has%20already%20met%20Governor%20Shiv%20Pratap%20Shukla%20amid%20buzz%20that%20it%20may%20bring%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20the%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%20government.%20Here's%20a%20look%20at%20how%20BJP%20pulled%20off%20a%20stunner%20and%20altered%20turned%20the%20tables%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Were%20Numbers%20Stacked%20Up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2068-member%20House%20has%2040%20MLAs%20from%20Congress%2C%2025%20from%20BJP%20and%20three%20Independents.%20The%20Congress%20chose%20senior%20lawyer%20Abhishek%20Singhvi%20as%20its%20candidate.%20The%20BJP%2C%20despite%20being%20at%20a%20numerical%20disadvantage%2C%20forced%20a%20contest%20by%20fielding%20veteran%20politician%20Harsh%20Mahajan%2C%20earlier%20with%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Premonition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20voting%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Sukhu%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%2040%20MLAs%20and%20will%20get%20all%20votes%20%26quot%3Bif%20no%20one%20gets%20sold%26quot%3B.%20The%20rider%20underlined%20the%20Congress's%20fears%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20a%20plan.%20State%20minister%20Harshwardhan%20Chauhan%20was%20more%20articulate.%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20has%20only%2025%20MLAs.%20Even%20without%20numbers%2C%20BJP%20is%20fielding%20their%20candidate.%20This%20means%20they're%20planning%20horse-trading%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20Congress%20also%20issued%20a%20whip%20for%20its%20MLAs%20to%20prevent%20cross-voting%2C%20a%20move%20the%20BJP%20called%20%26quot%3Bunethical%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Shock%20Result%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20counting%2C%20both%20Mr%20Singvi%20and%20Mr%20Mahajan%20were%20tied%20at%2034%20votes%20each%20-%20meaning%20six%20Congress%20MLAs%20and%20three%20Independents%20voted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BJP%20candidate.%20What%20followed%20was%20a%20tie-breaker%20by%20a%20draw%20of%20lots%2C%20and%20the%20BJP's%20Harsh%20Mahajan%20got%20an%20Upper%20House%20ticket%20despite%20all%20odds.%C2%A0According%20to%20a%20former%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%2C%20the%20draw%20of%20lots%20in%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election%20tie-breaker%20is%20an%20elimination%20pick%2C%20meaning%20that%20the%20person%20whose%20name%20is%20on%20the%20slip%20gets%20eliminated%20and%20the%20other%20wins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Reactions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20his%20shocking%20defeat%2C%20Mr%20Singvi%20said%20the%20election%20had%20%26quot%3Btaught%20me%20a%20lesson%2C%20how%20people%20can%20change%20their%20principles%20and%20ideologies%20overnight%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20nine%20MLAs%20who%20cross-voted%20had%20dinner%20with%20us%20on%20Monday%20night.%20Three%20of%20them%20also%20had%20breakfast%20with%20us%20in%20the%20morning.%20But%20they%20voted%20against%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNormally%2C%20in%20a%20draw%20of%20lots%2C%20the%20name%20that%20is%20taken%20out%20is%20that%20of%20the%20winner%2C%20but%20under%20the%20strange%20rule%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20which%20I%20came%20to%20know%20about%20only%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20name%20of%20the%20candidate%20taken%20out%2C%20which%20was%20mine%2C%20lost%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWinner%20Harsh%20Majahan%20said%20the%20victory%20belongs%20to%20BJP.%C2%A0%26quot%3BCross-voting%20was%20done%20because%20MLAs%20were%20verbal%20about%20being%20unhappy%20with%20the%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Aftermath%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%2024%20hours%2C%20the%20fight%20for%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20battle%20of%20survival%20for%20the%20Sukhu%20government.%20The%20BJP%20claims%20that%20the%20state%20government%20has%20lost%20the%20confidence%20of%20the%20House.%20The%20six%20rebel%20MLAs%20were%20taken%20away%20by%20Haryana%20police%2C%20Mr%20Sukhu%20said%20last%20night.%20The%20MLAs%20have%20been%20reportedly%20lodged%20at%20a%20resort%20in%20Panchkula%20and%20have%20met%20Himachal%20BJP%20chief%20Rajeev%20Bindal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20recent%20political%20point%20of%20view%20of%20the%20developments%20that%20have%20taken%20place%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20it%20can%20be%20said%20that%20the%20state%20government%20has%20lost%20the%20moral%20right%20to%20stay%20in%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Jai%20Ram%20Thakur%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20informed%20the%20Governor%20about%20what%20happened%20in%20the%20Assembly%20recently.%20We%20informed%20him%20about%20the%20behaviour%20of%20the%20Speaker%20towards%20the%20Opposition%20MLAs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20about%20how%20many%20Congress%20legislators%20are%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20tell%20you%20this%20now.%20I%20just%20want%20to%20say%20that%20Congress%20has%20lost%20mandate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709095980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F8spet5o8_sukhvinder-singh-sukhu_625x300_28_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fabhishek-singhvi-sukhvinder-singh-sukhu-rajya-sabha-election-himachal-crisis-premonition-betrayal-and-hard-luck-how-congress-lost-himachal-plot-5141529%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20election%20to%20one%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat%20has%20upset%20the%20power%20equations%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%20The%20Congress%2C%20which%20had%20a%20comfortable%20majority%20of%2040%20in%20a%2068-member%20Assembly%2C%20is%20now%20firefighting%20to%20save%20its%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%