ve%20sequenced%20genomes%20of%2010%2C000%20Indians%20from%20diverse%20communities%20to%20create%20a%20database%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20gene-based%20remedies%2C%20with%20Union%20Science%20and%20Technology%20Minister%20Jitendra%20Singh%20calling%20it%20a%20watershed%20moment%20for%20science%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20function%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20genome%20study%20or%20sequencing%20is%20going%20to%20determine%20the%20future%20healthcare%20strategies%20across%20the%20world%2C%20both%20therapeutically%20and%20prophylactically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20there%20is%20a%20pressing%20need%20for%20finding%20Indian%20solutions%20to%20Indian%20problems%20as%20the%20country%20emerges%20as%20a%20frontline%20nation%20in%20the%20comity%20of%20scientifically-advanced%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20lauded%20the%20Department%20of%20Biotechnology%20for%20the%20ambitious%20goal%20to%20identify%20and%20catalogue%20the%20genetic%20variations%20of%20diverse%20Indian%20populations%20by%20sequencing%20the%20whole%20genome%20of%2010%2C000%20healthy%20individuals%20from%2099%20communities%2C%20representing%20all%20major%20linguistic%20and%20social%20groups%2C%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20population%20of%201.3%20billion%20consists%20of%20more%20than%204%2C600%20population%20groups%2C%20and%20many%20of%20them%20are%20endogamous%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20factors%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20genetic%20diversity%20of%20the%20current%20population.%20Thus%2C%20the%20Indian%20population%20harbours%20distinct%20variations%20and%2C%20often%2C%20many%20disease-causing%20mutations%20are%20amplified%20within%20some%20of%20these%20groups.%20Therefore%2C%20findings%20from%20population-based%20or%20disease-based%20human%20genetics%20research%20from%20other%20populations%20of%20the%20world%20cannot%20be%20extrapolated%20to%20Indians%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECreating%20a%20database%20of%20Indian%20genomes%20means%20that%20researchers%20anywhere%20can%20learn%20about%20genetic%20variants%20that%20are%20unique%20to%20India's%20population%20groups%20and%20use%20that%20to%20customise%20drugs%20and%20therapies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%2C%20China%20and%20the%20US%20are%20among%20the%20countries%20that%20have%20programmes%20to%20sequence%20at%20least%201%2C00%2C000%20of%20their%20genomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProf%20Y%20Narahari%20and%20Dr%20K%20Thangaraj%2C%20the%20joint%20coordinators%20of%20GenomeIndia%2C%20said%20beyond%20the%20sheer%20scale%20of%20sequencing%20and%20establishing%20a%20reference%20genome%2C%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20biobank%20housing%2020%2C000%20blood%20samples%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Brain%20Research%2C%20coupled%20with%20data%20archiving%20at%20the%20Indian%20Biological%20Data%20Centre%2C%20exemplify%20the%20project's%20commitment%20to%20transparency%2C%20collaboration%20and%20future%20research%20endeavours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20is%20being%20stored%20at%20the%20Indian%20Biological%20Data%20Centre%20set%20up%20by%20Union%20government's%20Department%20of%20Biotechnology%20at%20the%20Regional%20Centre%20for%20Biotechnology%2C%20Faridabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709085600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-04%2Fernv9f3_genome-sequencing_625x300_17_April_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2F10-000-genomes-of-indian-population-sequenced-centre-5139545%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Scientists%20on%20Tuesday%20announced%20that%20they%20have%20sequenced%20genomes%20of%2010%2C000%20Indians%20from%20diverse%20communities%20to%20create%20a%20database%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20gene-based%20remedies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%