%20great%20place%20to%20raise%20a%20family.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20kids%20are%20old%20enough%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20plan%20to%20get%20them%20into%20judo%20gear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20judo%20that%20first%20sparked%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmove-between-us-georgia-japan-quality-life-better-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterest%20in%20Japan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20was%20enrolled%20in%20an%20after-school%20class%20when%20I%20was%204%2C%20and%20it%20turned%20into%20a%20constant%20that%20brought%20discipline%20to%20my%20childhood.%20The%20cultivation%20of%20both%20physical%20and%20mental%20strength%20and%20the%20emphasis%20on%20manners%20shaped%20my%20daily%20life.%20I%20practiced%20for%20the%20next%2013%20years%2C%20in%20Cape%20Town%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20where%20I%20grew%20up.%20My%20fascination%20with%20the%20martial%20art%20grew%20over%20the%20years%20and%20I%20was%20determined%20to%20visit%20its%20birthplace%20one%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20never%20attained%20an%20Olympian%20level%20of%20success%20in%20the%20sport%2C%20it%20wasn't%20judo%20that%20brought%20me%20here%20%E2%80%94%20but%20rather%20the%20Japan%20Exchange%20and%20Teaching%20(JET)%20Programme.%20I%20came%20over%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-know-before-moving-to-japan-westerner-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteach%20English%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20public%20high%20school%20in%20my%20early%2020s%20and%20did%20that%20for%20four%20years%20before%20moving%20on%20to%20other%20adventures%20in%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Ali%2C%20my%20now%20wife%2C%20and%20I%20matched%20up%20on%20a%20dating%20app%20in%20early%202020%2C%20I%20found%20out%20that%20it%20was%20JET%20that%20brought%20her%20to%20Japan%20in%20her%20early%2020s%20as%20well.%20She%20had%20taken%20up%20judo%20as%20a%20kid%20in%20her%20own%20hometown%20in%20Canada.%20Ali's%20classes