lt%3D%5C%22Brother%20and%20babies%20sleeping%20on%20a%20futon%20in%20Japan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65dda1da90413ab8e1d70624%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFinn%20gave%20birth%20to%20their%20daughter%20in%202022%2C%20and%20her%20partner%20carried%20their%20son%20the%20following%20year.%3Cp%3ECarey%20Finn%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20both%20gave%20birth%20at%20the%20same%20clinic%3B%20a%20lovely%20little%20place%20staffed%20primarily%20by%20midwives.%20I%20transferred%20there%20at%2027%20weeks%20pregnant%2C%20on%20the%20recommendation%20of%20our%20doula.%20I%20gave%20up%20the%20option%20for%20an%20epidural%20at%20a%20university%20hospital%20%E2%80%94%20where%20I%20had%20felt%20pressured%20to%20be%20in%20the%20closet%20%E2%80%94%20in%20favor%20of%20somewhere%20we%20could%20be%20ourselves.%20The%20birth%20clinic%20provided%20such%20an%20affirming%20experience%20that%20Ali%20then%20decided%20to%20give%20birth%20there%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20acceptance%20of%20our%20medical%20team%2C%20however%2C%20the%20Japanese%20birth%20certificates%20that%20we%20received%20list%20each%20of%20us%20as%20a%20single%20mom.%20Our%20local%20governments%20did%20what%20they%20could%20to%20get%20us%20both%20on%20the%20paperwork%2C%20but%20until%20the%20national%20laws%20change%2C%20we%20have%20to%20exist%20in%20a%20strange%20and%20unsettling%20space.%20Fortunately%2C%20we%20are%20recognized%20as%20the%20legal%20parents%20of%20both%20children%20by%20Canada%20and%20South%20Africa%2C%20though%20even%20that%20took%20a%20bit%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EJapan%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20places%20in%20the%20world%20to%20raise%20kids%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Couple%20in%20winter%20clothes%20and%20two%20children%20in%20a%20Japanese%20inn%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65dd9f8360801