ers%2C%20but%20the%20best%20players%20are%20often%20overbooked%20and%20on%20the%20move%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CSIS%20report%20said.%20%26quot%3BRather%20than%20directly%20relying%20on%20human%20players%20sitting%20around%20a%20table%20to%20play%20a%20game%2C%20the%20twenty-first-century%20analyst%20can%20use%20generative%20AI%20and%20LLMs%20to%20create%20game%20agents.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETalking%20with%20BI%20about%20the%20opportunities%20available%20with%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20Atalan%20said%20that%20with%20the%20right%20prompting%20and%20data%20curation%2C%20AI%20could%20assist%20players%20by%20contributing%20%26quot%3Bdifferent%20perspectives%20from%20different%20allies%26quot%3B%20and%20provide%20probability%20distribution%20and%20other%20data%20points%20in%20a%20wargame.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWargaming%20is%20often%20misunderstood%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20predict%20outcomes%2C%20but%20Atalan%2C%20along%20with%20other%20experts%20emphasize%20that%20wargaming%20is%20not%20about%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20about%20for%20the%20players%2C%20for%20the%20different%20teams%2C%20for%20the%20stakeholders%2C%20to%20see%20what%20are%20their%20range%20of%20policy%20options%2C%20what%20are%20the%20possible%20opportunities%20and%20challenges%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20Marine%20Corps%20officers%20assigned%20to%20the%2022nd%20Marine%20Expeditionary%20Unit%20(MEU)%20conduct%20a%20wargaming%20scenario%20aboard%20Amphibious%20Assault%20Ship%20USS%20Kearsarge%20(LHD%203)%2C%20Oct.%2022%2C%202021%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65de620e6080194819faa455%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20Marine%20Corps%20officers%20assigned%20to%20the%2022nd%20Marine%20Expeditionary%20Unit%20(MEU)%20conduct%20a%20wargaming%20scenario%20aboard%20Amphibious%20Assault%20Ship%20USS%20Kearsarge%20(LHD%203)%2C%20Oct.%2022%2C%202021.%3Cp%3EUS%20Marine%20Corps%20photo%20by%20Cpl.%20Yvonna%20Guyette%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20military%20began%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.usni.org%2F2015%2F03%2F18%2Fdocument-memo-to-pentagon-leadership-on-wargaming%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eputting%3C%2Fa%3E%20increased%20emphasis%20on%20the%20need%20for%20wargaming%20in%202015%20and%20over%20the%20years%2C%20in%20concert%20with%20the%20hype%2C%20there%20has%20been%20growing%20interest%20in%20the%20possibilities%20of%20AI.%20In%20February%202023%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20the%20US%20military%20let%20AI%20successfully%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-military-let-ai-fly-fighter-battle-simulated-enemies-combat-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epilot%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20fighter%20jet%20and%20engage%20in%20simulated%20air-to-air%20combat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20growing%20realization%20the%20two%20interests%20could%20be%20combined%20to%20leverage%20the%20potential%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWargaming%20and%20simulation%20continue%20to%20be%20crucial%20tools%20for%20decision-makers%20in%20Defence%2C%26quot%3B%20a%202023%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcetas.turing.ac.uk%2Fpublications%2Fartificial-intelligence-wargaming%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20London-based%20Alan%20Turing%20Institute%20concluded.%20%26quot%3BThey%20can%20be%20used%20to%20train%20personnel%20for%20future%20conflict%2C%20and%20offer%20insights%20on%20critical%20decisions%20in%20warfighting%2C%20peace%20negotiations%2C%20arms%20control%2C%20and%20emergency%20response.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20also%20found%20that%20using%20AI%20for%20wargaming%20could%20potentially%20cut%20down%20the%20number%20of%20players%20needed%2C%20speed%20up%20games%2C%20produce%20new%20strategies%2C%20better%20immerse%20players%20in%20games%2C%20and%20speed%20up%20game%20completion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20also%20has%20its%20limits%20in%20this%20space.%20A%20recent%20RAND%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rand.org%2Fpubs%2Fresearch_reports%2FRRA1722-4.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20AI%20may%20not%20work%20as%20well%20in%20a%20wargame%20if%20the%20digital%20infrastructure%20of%20a%20game%20is%20restricted%20or%20if%20AI%20can't%20directly%20interact%20with%20the%20computational%20models%20and%20simulations%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWargaming%20expert%20Ivanka%20Barzashka%20has%20also%20raised%20concerns%20that%20AI%20may%20obscure%20explanations%20for%20actions%2C%20potentially%20leading%20to%20faulty%20conclusions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20current%20landscape%20of%20human-centric%20wargaming%2C%20combined%20with%20AI%20algorithms%2C%20faces%20a%20notable%20%26quot%3Bblack%20box%26quot%3B%20challenge%2C%20where%20the%20reasoning%20behind%20certain%20outcomes%20remains%20unclear%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebulletin.org%2F2023%2F12%2Fwargames-and-ai-a-dangerous-mix-that-needs-ethical-oversight%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20a%20post%20for%20The%20Bulletin%20of%20the%20Atomic%20Scientists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarzashka%20argued%20that%20%26quot%3Bthis%20obscurity%2C%20alongside%20potential%20biases%20in%20AI%20training%20data%20and%20wargame%20design%2C%20highlights%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20ethical%20governance%20and%20accountability%20in%20this%20evolving%20domain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221397%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22NPS%20students%20participate%20in%20analytic%20wargames%20they%20designed%20to%20explore%20solutions%20for%20some%20of%20DoD's%20most%20pressing%20national%20security%20concerns%20at%20a%202018%20event.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65de687090413ab8e1d74de3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22934%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENPS%20students%20participate%20in%20analytic%20wargames%