ving%20beyond%20the%20Western%20outsider's%20perspective%20to%20survey%20a%20fracturing%20society%20that%20is%20just%20as%20baffled%20by%20this%20interloper's%20ways%20as%20he%20is%20by%20theirs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F02%2F26%2Farts%2Ftelevision%2Fshogun-review.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times'%20Mike%20Hale%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20the%20showrunners%20%26quot%3Bhave%20recalibrated%20the%20narrative%2C%20however%2C%20moving%20Blackthorne's%20point%20of%20view%20down%20in%20the%20mix%20and%20elevating%20the%20roles%20of%20many%20of%20the%20Japanese%20characters%2C%20particularly%20Toda%20Mariko%2C%20the%20noblewoman%20who%20becomes%20Blackthorne's%20translator%20and%20love%20interest%2C%20and%20Yoshii%20Toranaga%2C%20the%20lord%20who%20both%20protects%20and%20manipulates%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ign.com%2Farticles%2Fshogun-review-fx-hulu%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIGN's%20Samantha%20Nelson%3C%2Fa%3E%20wrote%20that%20%26quot%3BSh%C5%8Dgun%20could%20easily%20have%20become%20a%20repeat%20of%20'The%20Last%20Samurai%2C'%20where%20Sanada%20played%20mentor%20to%20another%20transplanted-Westerner%20protagonist%2C%20but%20the%20series%20takes%20more%20of%20an%20ensemble%20approach%20rather%20than%20centering%20the%20story%20on%20John's%20experiences.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EReviews%20praised%20Hiroyuki%20Sanada's%20performance%20as%20Toranaga%20Yoshii%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hiroyuki%20sanada%20as%20yoshii%20toranaga%2C%20a%20man%20in%20armor%20sitting%20on%20a%20horse%20on%20top%20of%20a%20hill%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65de52ad6080194819fa9b20%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHiroyuki%20Sanada%20as%20Yoshii%20Toranaga%20in%20%26quot%3BSh%C5%8Dgun.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EKatie%20Yu%2FFX%3C%2Fp%3E%3