20says%20elements%20of%20the%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20vigilantes%20have%20ensured%20that%20there%20is%20a%20distinction%20between%20what%20happens%20officially%20and%20what%20happens%20unofficially%20and%20even%20illegally.%20Often%20the%20civilian%20government%20is%20the%20front%20facade%2C%20but%20at%20times%20it%20even%20seems%20redundant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20handling%20of%20the%20economy%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cquasi-loss%20decade%E2%80%9D%2C%20Jaffrelot%20said%20that%20while%20MSMEs%2C%20youths%2C%20farmers%2C%20Dalits%20and%20Adivasis%20have%20either%20lost%20out%20or%20stagnated%20under%20Modi%2C%20oligarchs%20have%20gained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20claims%20on%20the%20economic%20front%20%E2%80%9Care%20not%20supported%20by%20data%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20Thomas%20Piketty%2C%20Jaffrelot%20said%20India%20is%20the%20most%20unequal%20country%20in%20the%20world%20after%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%20in%20the%20interview%20he%20described%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20economic%20policies%20as%20%E2%80%9Cpro-rich%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20attitude%20to%20Muslims%2C%20Jaffrelot%20said%20%E2%80%9Che%20looks%20at%20Muslims%20as%20descendants%20of%20converts%20or%20foreigners%E2%80%9D.%20Jaffrelot%20said%20he%20treats%20them%20as%20second-class%20citizens%20who%20should%20be%20%E2%80%98obliterated%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98ghettoised%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaffrelot%20said%20the%20majoritarian%20attitude%20means%20%E2%80%9CMuslims%20are%20at%20the%20bottom%20or%20margins%20of%20the%20social%20pyramid%E2%80%9D.%20He%20said%20%E2%80%9CMuslims%20are%20de%20facto%20second-class%20citizens%20becoming%20de%20jure%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20relation%20to%20a%20question%20about%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20participation%20in%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20consecration%2C%20when%20he%20emerged%20as%20the%20high-priest%20of%20Hindu%20nationalism%2C%20Jaffrelot%20said%20%E2%80%9Csecularism%20is%20dying%E2%80%9D.%20He%20called%20it%20%E2%80%9Ca%20dead%20letter%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20not%20Hinduism%20but%20%E2%80%9CHindutva%20is%20the%20de%20facto%20ideology%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20personality%20cult%20surrounding%20Modi%2C%20Jaffrelot%20first%20compared%20it%20to%20the%20personality%20cult%20under%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20but%20added%20that%20for%20two%20reasons%2C%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20personality%20cult%20is%20greater%20and%20also%20more%20disturbing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%20did%20not%20differentiate%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims.%20Second%2C%20she%20did%20not%20have%20access%20to%20the%20modern%20day%20technologies%20available%20to%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20Nehru%2C%20Jaffrelot%20said%20that%20he%20%E2%80%9Cthinks%E2%80%9D%20that%20Modi%20does%20have%20a%20complex%20about%20Nehru%2C%20who%20he%20is%20constantly%20targeting%20and%20belittling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaffrelot%20said%20that%20if%20Modi%20is%20re-elected%2C%20he%20does%20envisage%20definite%20steps%20being%20taken%20towards%20creating%20a%20Hindu%20%3Cem%3Erashtra%3C%2Fem%3E%20(nation).%20He%20says%20they%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20taken%20immediately%20after%20the%20re-election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20Jaffrelot%20said%20%E2%80%9CModi%20has%20no%20successor%E2%80%9D%2C%20adding%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20very%20difficult%20to%20succeed%20a%20man%20like%20Modi%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20understand%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20and%20political%20personality%2C%20I%20cannot%20strongly%20enough%20recommend%20this%20interview.%20Jaffrelot%20has%20spoken%20analytically%2C%20but%20also%20with%20illustrative%20detail.%20He%E2%80%99s%20measured%20but%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20critical.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20the%20interview%20is%20a%20%3Cem%3Etour%20d%E2%80%99horizon%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20situation%20today%20as%20well%20as%20a%20perceptive%20analysis%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20personality%20and%20political%20qualities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeeks%20before%20the%20next%20general%20election%2C%20I%20do%20believe%20this%20is%20an%20interview%20you%20must%20see%20to%20understand%20where%20we%20are%2C%20what%20sort%20of%20person%20is%20our%20prime%20minister%2C%20what%20are%20the%20implications%20of%20the%20policies%20he%E2%80%99s%20followed%2C%20their%20success%20or%20lack%20of%20and%2C%20at%20the%20end%2C%20what%20to%20expect%20if%20he%20wins%20as%20well%20as%20what%20to%20expect%20when%20he%20finally%20departs%20the%20political%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FsGRQOR0P4c8%3Fsi%3DL8GVJ1jU3CXGLIOY%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20you%2C%20I%20give%20below%20the%20list%20of%20questions%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20been%20prime%20minister%20for%20ten%20years%20and%20he%20hopes%20to%20add%20another%20five%20at%20the%20forthcoming%20elections.%20Let%20me%20start%20by%20asking%20what%20is%20your%20assessment%20of%20his%20performance%20as%20prime%20minister%20over%20the%20last%20decade%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E2.%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20frequently%20boasts%20of%20his%20handling%20of%20the%20economy.%20He%20says%20he%E2%80%99s%20made%20India%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20fifth-biggest%20economy%20and%20lifted%20250%20million%20out%20of%20poverty.%20His%20critics%20talk%20about%20unprecedented%20levels%20of%20unemployment%2C%20increasing%20inequality%20and%20K-shaped%20growth.%20What%E2%80%99s%20your%20opinion%20of%20how%20Modi%20has%20handled%20the%20economy%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E3.%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20domin