he%20state%20government%20has%20already%20arrested%2020%20people%20and%20that%20Shahjahan%20will%20also%20be%20arrested%20now%20that%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20has%20said%20that%20there%20is%20no%20stay%20on%20taking%20action%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20West%20Bengal%20police%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20being%20partisan%20and%20acting%20on%20Mamata%20%5BBanerjee%5D%E2%80%99s%20instructions.%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20the%20BJP%20that%20the%20advocate%20general%20has%20informed%20the%20court%20that%2020%20arrests%20have%20been%20made%20in%20Sandeshkhali%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dev.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20are%20accusing%20the%20West%20Bengal%20police%20of%20being%20partisan%2C%20we%20want%20to%20ask%20them%2C%20who%20is%20Shibu%20Hazra%3F%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20proved%20that%20whether%20it%20is%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20mothers%2C%20sisters%20or%20elderly%2C%20if%20there%20is%20any%20injustice%2C%20she%20will%20take%20action%20and%20not%20look%20at%20any%20party%20affiliation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHazra%2C%20a%20TMC%20block-level%20president%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20North%2024%20Parganas%20zilla%20parishad%2C%20was%20named%20by%20multiple%20women%20in%20serious%20sexual%20harassment%20cases%20and%20was%20only%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fsandeshkhali-unrest-as-women-led-protests-escalate-tmcs-outsider-claims-find-little-resonance%5C%22%3Earrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20month%20after%20the%20state%20government%20faced%20pressure%20from%20the%20opposition%2C%20including%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20a%20question%20by%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fi%3Eon%20why%20the%20state%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20act%20against%20Shahjahan%20despite%20allegations%20of%20land-grab%20and%20attacks%20on%20women%20being%20raised%20in%20the%20West%20Bengal%20assembly%20as%20far%20back%20as%20in%202012%2C%20the%20TMC%20leaders%20said%20that%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20had%20not%20been%20filed%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPolice%20file%20a%20complaint%20if%20there%20is%20an%20FIR.%20Tomorrow%2C%20I%20can%20stand%20and%20say%20something%20in%20front%20of%20the%20chief%20justice%20of%20India%2C%20but%20the%20police%20will%20investigate%20only%20when%20an%20FIR%20is%20filed%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Gokhale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20by%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fi%3Eabout%20why%20the%20issue%20being%20raised%20in%20the%20assembly%20did%20not%20warrant%20any%20action%2C%20Ghose%20added%20that%20now%20that%20FIRs%20have%20been%20registered%2C%20the%20police%20investigation%20has%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20that%20FIRs%20have%20come%2C%20the%20police%20are%20investigating%20and%20arresting%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%3Ci%3E%20The%20Telegraph%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fwest-bengal%2Fsandeshkhali-alert-in-records-former-cpm-mla-nirapada-sardar-took-up-atrocities-10-years-ago-in-house%2Fcid%2F2002964%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20citing%20official%20assembly%20records%20that%20CPI(M)%20MLA%20Nirapada%20Sardar%2C%20who%20represented%20Sandeshkhali%20from%202011%20to%202016%2C%20had%20raised%20those%20issues%20at%20least%20thrice%20%E2%80%93%20twice%20in%202012%20and%20once%20in%202013%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESardar%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20on%20February%2011%20on%20charges%20of%20fomenting%20trouble%20in%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20was%20granted%20bail%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20is%20proactively%20engaging%20on%20women%E2%80%99s%20issues%20across%20the%20state.%20In%20every%20area%2C%20the%20TMC%20government%20is%20looking%20to%20address%20grievances%20that%20are%20brought%20by%20the%20women%20of%20the%20area%20and%20when%20the%20complaint%20was%20registered%2C%20the%20government%20did%20act%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ghose%20to%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGokhale%20said%20that%20the%20state%20government%20had%20not%20acted%20against%20Shahjahan%20due%20to%20a%20February%207%20order%20by%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20restraining%20any%20action%20against%20him.%20He%20went%20on%20to%20take%20aim%20at%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20February%207%2C%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20in%20its%20order%20clearly%20restrained%20West%20Bengal%20police%20from%20taking%20any%20action%20against%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan.%20February%208%20onwards%20every%20single%20day%2C%20one%20BJP%20minister%2C%20one%20BJP%20MLA%2C%20somebody%20from%20this%20commission%20or%20that%20commission%20started%20visiting%20Sandeshkhali%20every%20single%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYesterday%20%5BFebruary%2027%5D%2C%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20issued%20a%20clarification%20that%20the%20West%20Bengal%20police%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsandeshkhali-updates-tmc-sheikh-shahjahan%5C%22%3Efree%20to%20take%20action%20against%20Shahjahan%20Sheikh%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20happened%20at%2012%3A30%20in%20the%20afternoon%20%5Band%5D%20by%201-1%3A30%20pm%2C%20an%20FIR%20had%20been%20filed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20West%20Bengal%20police%20are%20very%20confident%20that%20they%20will%20nab%20him%20in%20a%20few%20days.%20This%20is%20not%20Nirav%20Modi%20or%20Mehul%20Choksi%2C%20where%20they%20take%20a%20foreign%20passport%20and%20leave%20the%20country.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20BJP%20government%20but%20a%20TMC%20government.%20He%20will%20be%20brought%20to%20book%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShahjahan%20has%20been%20absconding%20since%20January%205%2C%20when%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20officials%20who%20were%20investigating%20an%20alleged%20ration%20distribution%20scam%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-bengals-sandeshkhali-controversial-tmc-leader-sheikh-shahjahans-hold-is-powerful%5C%22%3Eattacked%20at%20his%20residence%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDev%20said%20that%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20will%20be%20visiting%20Sandeshkhali%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20%5Bthe%20BJP%5D%20did%20not%20remove%20Brij%20Bhushan%20%5BSharan%20Singh%5D%2C%20you%20garlanded%20Bilkis%20Bano%E2%80%99s%20rapists.%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20them%20that%20her%20%5BBanerjee%E2%80%99s%5D%20only%20allegiance%20is%20the%20people%20of%20Bengal%20and%20those%20who%20do%20injustice%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Bengal%20will%20face%20action%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLet%20me%20assure%20you%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20Abishek%20Banerjee%20%5BBanerjee%E2%80%99s%20nephew%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%5D%20will%20go%20there%2C%20let%20us%20see%20when%20the%20PM%20will%20go%20to%20Manipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709048245000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27210539%2FTrinamool-press.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffacing-fire-tmc-leaders-say-allegiance-only-to-people-of-bengal-shahjahan-arrest-soon%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20response%20to%20a%20question%20by%20The%20Wire%20on%20why%20the%20state%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20act%20against%20Shahjahan%20despite%20allegations%20of%20land-grab%20and%20attacks%20on%20women%20being%20raised%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20as%20far%20back%20as%20in%202012%2C%20TMC%20leaders%20said%20that%20an%20FIR%20had%20not%20been%20filed%20then.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffacing-fire-tmc-leaders-say-allegiance-only-to-people-of-bengal-shahjahan-arrest-soon%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Takeda%20injects%20hope%3A%20Dengue%