school%20documents%20in%202019.%20Allegedly%2C%20she%20was%20kidnapped%20by%20Muslim%20students%20earlier%20that%20year%20and%20has%20remained%20untraceable.%20However%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20investigated%20and%20found%20that%20Muskan%20herself%20stated%20in%20an%20affidavit%20that%20she%20erroneously%20marked%20her%20religion%20as%20Muslim%20on%20her%2010th-grade%20application%20form%20when%20she%20enrolled%20herself%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2022%2C%20Firoz%20Khan%2C%20Mirza%20Mujahid%2C%20and%20Shabana%20received%20notifications%20of%20their%20suspension%20via%20WhatsApp.%20Mirza%20Mujahid%2C%20who%20has%20taught%20at%20the%20school%20for%20eight%20years%2C%20expressed%20dismay%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20fact-checking%20prior%20to%20their%20suspension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFiroz%20Khan%20joined%20the%20school%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20while%20Shabana%20had%20only%20been%20there%20for%20three%20months%20and%20claimed%20no%20knowledge%20of%20Muskan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20there%20are%20265%20students%20enrolled%20in%20the%20school%2C%20alongside%2015%20faculty%20members%2C%20including%20three%20who%20are%20Muslim.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20those%20questioning%20us%2C%20I%20urge%20them%20to%20inquire%20about%20the%20other%2012%20Hindu%20faculty%20members%20regarding%20our%20conduct.%20We%20are%20being%20singled%20out%20solely%20because%20we%20belong%20to%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Firoz%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20message%2C%20Dilawar%20emphasised%20his%20stance%20against%20religious%20conversion%20and%20vowed%20to%20dismiss%20teachers%20found%20guilty%20after%20further%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20Dilawar%20to%20inquire%20whether%20the%20action%20taken%20had%20undergone%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20and%20yielded%20conclusive%20evidence%20against%20the%20faculty%20members.%20Dilawar%E2%80%99s%20spokesperson%2C%20Prapat%20Si