r-hanskhali-mamata-love-affair-comment-1936993-2022-04-13%5C%22%3ETrinamool%20supremo%20had%20raised%20doubts%20about%20the%20gangrape-murder%20of%20a%2014-year-old%20girl%20in%20Nadia%20district%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20victim%2C%20invited%20to%20a%20birthday%20party%20by%20the%20son%20of%20a%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20in%20Hanshkhali%20was%20allegedly%20gang-raped%20by%20the%20youth%20and%20his%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20later%20died%20due%20to%20excessive%20bleeding%2C%20and%20family%20members%20were%20reportedly%20prevented%20from%20seeking%20medical%20help.%20Following%20her%20death%20local%20Trinamool%20workers%20attacked%20the%20family%2C%20pointing%20a%20gun%20and%20forcefully%20cremated%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20later%20used%20the%20child%20helpline%20to%20raise%20the%20complaint.%20Banerjee%2C%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20then%20West%20Bengal%20police%20chief%20Manoj%20Malaviya%2C%20suggested%20the%20girl%20had%20an%20affair%20with%20the%20accused%2C%20leading%20to%20sharp%20criticism%20from%20opposition%20parties.%20The%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20subsequently%20transferred%20the%20case%20to%20the%20CBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20a%2020-year-old%20college%20student%20was%20abducted%2C%20gang-raped%2C%20and%20murdered%20in%20Kamduni%20village%2C%20located%2016%20km%20from%20Barasat%20in%20the%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fmamata-banerjee-slams-kamduni-rape-protesters-gets-angry-send-off%2Farticleshow%2F20638913.cms%5C%22%3E.%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fmamata-banerjee-slams-kamduni-rape-protesters-gets-angry-send-off%2Farticleshow%2F20638913.cms%5C%22%3ETen%20days%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20chief%20minister%20Banerjee%20visited%20the%20victim%E2%80%99s%20family%20in%20Kamduni%20and%20encountered%20a%20group%20of%20protesting%20women%20whom%20she%20accused%20of%2