20to%20the%20dark%20alleys%20of%20cash%20funding%3F%20That%20is%20a%20legitimate%20concern.%20The%20government%20must%20consult%20all%20stakeholders%20in%20coming%20up%20with%20another%20alternative%20with%20strong%20sunshine%20clauses%20to%20address%20the%20rot%20that%20political%20funding%20has%20fallen%20into%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20offers%2C%20as%20a%20way%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asks%20pointedly%20about%20what%20will%20happen%20to%20the%20funds%20raised%20under%20the%20scheme%20which%20the%20top%20court%20described%20as%20%E2%80%9Cunconstitutional%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CFinally%2C%20will%20this%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20a%20case%20of%20closing%20the%20stables%20after%20the%20horses%20have%20bolted%3F%20What%20would%20be%20the%20nature%20and%20fate%20of%20funds%20raised%20under%20an%20%E2%80%98unconstitutional%E2%80%99%20scheme%3F%20Is%20the%20violator%20entitled%20to%20enjoy%20the%20fruits%20of%20the%20violation%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20goes%20on%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CMarch%2013%20is%20expected%20to%20lift%20the%20veil%20but%20will%20those%20blinded%20by%20the%20blaze%20of%20self-discovered%20glory%20see%20anything%20pernicious%3F%20Let%20not%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20impending%20elections%20cast%20a%20shadow%20on%20the%20SC%20judgement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20elections%20around%20the%20corner%20and%20a%20new%20Lok%20Sabha%20set%20to%20be%20constituted%20soon%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CLet%20us%20hope%20the%20new%20parliament%20will%20bring%20about%20a%20law%20showing%20full%20respect%20to%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20SC%20so%20that%20India%20can%20justifiably%20hail%20itself%20as%20the%20mother%20of%20democracy%20without%20being%20accused%20of%20giving%20democracy%20a%20stepmotherly%20treatment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20hoping%20for%20more%20transparency%20going%20forward%20in%20terms%20of%20how%20political%20parties%20operate%2C%20he%20writes%2C%20%E2%80%9CLet%20us%20hope%20there%20are%20no%20sudden%20c