m%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fitalian-priest-smells-bleach-in-chalice-to-avoid-apparent-mafia-threat-13082175%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fitalian-priest-smells-bleach-in-chalice-to-avoid-apparent-mafia-threat-13082175%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Animal%20Activists%20Question%20%E2%80%98Stray%20Dog%20Theory%E2%80%99%20in%20Delhi%20Mauling%20Incident%3B%20NHRC%20Issues%20Notices%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F09%2F6801981960_5f6b0d02ab_k.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Animal%20rights%20activists%20have%20contested%20the%20claim%20that%20stray%20dogs%20were%20responsible%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2F2-year-old-girl-mauled-to-death-by-five-stray-dogs-in-delhi-locals-allege-negligence%2Farticleshow%2F108000260.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Edeath%20of%20a%20toddler%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Tughlaq%20Lane%20area%20of%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20child%2C%20who%20was%20between%2016%20months%20and%20two%20years%20old%2C%20according%20to%20varying%20accounts%2C%20was%20reportedly%20mauled%20to%20death%20by%20a%20pack%20of%20dogs%20in%20the%20Dhobi%20Ghat%20area%20of%20the%20neighbourhood%20on%20Saturday%20(February%2024).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20in%20various%20newspapers%20have%20suggested%20that%20the%20child%20was%20sitting%20outside%20her%20house%20when%20%E2%80%9Cfour%20to%20five%20stray%20dogs%20attacked%20her%2C%20dragging%20her%20several%20metres%2C%20inflicting%20fatal%20injuries%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20animal%20rights%20activists%20and%20a%20few%20local%20residents%20have%20questioned%20the%20stray%20dog%20theory%20on%20several%20accounts%20in%20a%20press%20note%20released%20Tuesday%20(February%2027).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20alleged%20that%20Dhobi%20Ghat%2C%20where%20the%20child%20resided%20with%20her%20extended%20family%2C%20is%20a%20gated%20compound%20that%20community%20dogs%20could%20not%20have%20accessed.%20The%20lane%20has%20CCTV%20camera%20coverage%2C%20a%20lookout%20tower%20and%20a%20constant%20police%20vigil%20due%20to%20its%20proximity%20to%20BJP%20veteran%20L.K.%20Advani%E2%80%99s%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20activists%20also%20questioned%20how%20a%20child%20being%20dragged%20away%20by%20dogs%20was%20not%20immediately%20noticed%20in%20a%20heavily%20surveilled%20area%20such%20as%20this%2C%20adding%20that%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20lane%20had%20been%20cordoned%20off%20for%20a%20function%20and%20was%20full%20of%20catering%20staff%20and%20visitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20media%20reports%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthepatriot.in%2Fdelhi-ncr%2Ftwo-year-old-mauled-to-death-as-pack-of-stray-dogs-attack-her-drag-her-several-meters-46058%5C%22%3Eciting%20eyewitness%20accounts%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20also%20come%20under%20the%20scanner%20as%2C%20according%20to%20the%20note%2C%20the%20police%20found%20no%20eyewitnesses%20to%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20police%20officer%20to%20reach%20the%20hospital%20said%20that%20he%20found%20no%20eye-witnesses%20to%20the%20incident%20amongst%20the%20family.%20He%20has%20further%20recorded%20that%20upon%20returning%20to%20the%20site%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20he%20found%20no%20eye-witnesses%20amongst%20the%20crowd%20of%20residents%2C%20onlookers%2C%20visitors%20and%20others%20who%20were%20present%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20note%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnhrc.nic.in%2Fmedia%2Fpress-release%2Fnhrc-takes-suo-motu-cognizance-stray-dog-mauling-2-year-old-girl-new-delhi%5C%22%3ENational%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20(NHRC)%20announced%20on%20Tuesday%20(February%2027)%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20had%20taken%20cognisance%20of%20the%20reports%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20incident%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20an%20isolated%20case%E2%80%9D%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20had%20previously%20directed%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20civic%20authorities%20to%20control%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20stray%20dog%20population%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20relevant%20Union%20government%20rules%20following%20%E2%80%9Cearlier%20tragic%20incidents%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20said%20it%20had%20issued%20notices%20to%20officials%20in%20Delhi%20seeking%20a%20detailed%20report%20on%20the%20incident%20within%20six%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%E2%80%99s%20government%20%E2%80%9Cis%20expected%20to%20inform%20whether%20any%20relief%20has%20been%20given%20to%20the%20deceased%E2%80%99s%20next%20of%20kin%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20NHRC%20continued%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSimilar%20incidents%20have%20been%20reported%20from%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20in%20the%20recent%20past%20and%20as%20such%20this%20is%20not%20a%20problem%20for%20any%20one%20state%20or%20Union%20territory.%20The%20situation%20is%20grim%20and%20alarming%2C%20requiring%20immediate%20and%20effective%20action%20by%20the%20authorities%20without%20any%20delay%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20activists%2C%20the%20child%E2%80%99s%20family%20housed%20an%20unfriendly%20dog%20(a%20type%20of%20pit%20bull)%20that%20they%20used%20for%20breeding%20purposes.%20Questions%20have%20been%20raised%20around%20the%20pit%20bull%E2%80%99s%20involvement%20in%20the%20incident%20and%20if%20the%20child%20was%20left%20unattended%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20activists%20also%20raised%20concerns%20about%20unchecked%2C%20illegal%20breeding%20of%20dogs%20in%20Delhi%20and%20the%20conditions%20in%20which%20these%20animals%20are%20kept%20that%20leads%20to%20them%20being%20hostile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20request%20the%20authorities%20to%20examine%20all%20the%20surrounding%20CCTV%20footage%20before%20reaching%20any%20conclusion%20about%20this%20child%E2%80%99s%20death.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20evidence%2C%20footage%2C%20eye-%20witnesses%20or%20even%20a%20post-mortem%20report%2C%20every%20media%20story%20has%20unequivocally%20blamed%20the%20tragedy%20on%20the%20community%20dogs.%20As%20a%20result%20of%20this%20hate-mongering%2C%20two%20dogs%20of%20the%20area%20have%20already%20been%20bludgeoned%20to%20death%20in%20cold%20blood%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20note%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20activists%20said%20that%20since%20it%20is%20a%20high%20security%20area%2C%20it%20is%20reasonable%20to%20expect%20that%20irrefutable%20evidence%20can%20be%20found%20to%20determine%20what%20happened%20to%20the%20child%20instead%20of%20blaming%20it%20on%20stray%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20note%20was%20signed%20by%20Anjali%20Gopalan%2C%20managing%20trustee%2C%20All%20Creatures%20Great%20and%20Small%20and%20executive%20director%2C%20The%20Naz%20Foundation%20(India)%2C%20Geeta%20Seshamani%2C%20vice-president%2C%20Friendicoes%20and%20co-founder%2C%20Wildlife%20SOS%2C%20Ambika%20Shukla%2C%20trustee%2C%20People%20for%20Animals%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Percival%20Billimoria%2C%20Shernaz%20Italia%20and%20Freny%20Kodaiji%2C%20trustees%2C%20DogMatters%20as%20well%20as%20Tilak%20Nanda%20and%20Kavita%20Rai%20who%20are%20residents%20of%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709035952000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F09%2F6801981960_5f6b0d02ab_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fanimal-activists-question-stray-dog-theory-in-tughlaq-lane-mauling-incident%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20activists%20said%20that%20since%20it%20is%20a%20high%20security%20area%2C%20it%20is%20reasonable%20to%20expect%20that%20irrefutable%20evidence%20can%20be%20found%20to%20determine%20what%20happened%20to%20the%20child%20instead%20of%20blaming%20it%20on%20stray%20dogs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fanimal-activists-question-stray-dog-theory-in-tughlaq-lane-mauling-incident%22%2C%2