0all%20clinics%20were%20shut.%20We%20could%20only%20take%20PK%20for%20treatment%20on%20the%202nd%20(of%20January).%C2%A0Having%20a%20spinal%20compression%20and%20a%20broken%20leg%2C%20PK%20was%20paralysed.%20After%20much%20care%2C%20attention%20and%20physiotherapy%20for%20more%20than%20a%20month%2C%20PK%20started%20walking%2C%20running%20and%20playing.%20Although%20we%20were%20initially%20reluctant%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20adopt%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSnapinsta.app_331049538_8602486409823819_7158574811666658490_n_1080-1708958384.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Daaman%20Dog%20Shelter%20Home%20in%20Chennai%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSnapinsta.app_331049538_8602486409823819_7158574811666658490_n_1080-1708958384.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSnapinsta.app_331049538_8602486409823819_7158574811666658490_n_1080-1708958384-300x166.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSnapinsta.app_331049538_8602486409823819_7158574811666658490_n_1080-1708958384-500x276.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSnapinsta.app_331049538_8602486409823819_7158574811666658490_n_1080-1708958384-768x424.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSnapinsta.app_331049538_8602486409823819_7158574811666658490_n_1080-1708958384-150x83.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343232%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22596%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESarah%20and%20her%20husband%20Gerry%20spend%20their%20days%20taking%20care%20of%20these%20dogs.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5C