ing%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20device.%20%E2%80%9COur%20competitors%20charge%20about%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20for%20their%20device.%20We%20reduced%20the%20cost%20drastically%20so%20that%20patients%20in%20developing%20countries%20could%20also%20afford%20this%20care.%20Hospitals%20can%20buy%20our%20device%20for%20anywhere%20between%20Rs%2013%20lakh%20and%20Rs%2016%20lakh%20depending%20on%20the%20variant%20of%20the%20device.%20The%20hospitals%20thereafter%20charge%20between%20Rs%201%2C500%20and%20Rs%204%2C000%20per%20patient%20per%20session%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EReceived%20Rs%2030%20lakh%20Investment%20in%20Shark%20Tank%20India%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaghuveer%20says%20his%20goal%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20patients%20can%20get%20through%20the%20therapy%20without%20using%20a%20wig%20or%20a%20scarf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F5dFYUt_zzhc%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F5dFYUt_zzhc%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPost-chemotherapy%2C%20almost%20all%20patients%20experience%20complete%20hair%20loss.%20Even%20if%20the%20patient%20loses%2030%20or%