%20most%20of%20the%20students%20and%20residents%20hailed%20from%20villages%20near%20the%20Mohanpura%20Dam.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20construction%20of%20the%20dam%20forced%20these%20people%20to%20relocate.%20The%20Government%20built%20a%20few%20houses%20and%20roads%2C%20and%20labelled%20it%20Mohanpura%20Colony.%20However%20they%20did%20not%20create%20any%20employment%20for%20the%20people%20displaced%20who%20had%20lost%20their%20lands%20and%20had%20no%20avenue%20of%20income.%20So%20most%20of%20the%20people%20were%20worried%20about%20bringing%20food%20to%20the%20table%20at%20the%20time%2C%20and%20educational%20concerns%20were%20far%20from%20being%20in%20their%20mind%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fschool-8-1708436803.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Old%20school%20(top%20right)%20and%20the%20newly%20transformed%20school%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fschool-8-1708436803.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fschool-8-1708436803-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fschool-8-1708436803-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fschool-8-1708436803-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fschool-8-1708436803-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342503%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOld%20school%20(top%20right)%20and%20the%20newly%20transformed%20school.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CAlso%20while%20setting%20up%20the%20colony%20for%20the%20people%2C%20the%20villagers%20were%20given%20a%20broken-down%20building%20to%20be%20used%20for%20a%20school.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20almost%20more%20than%20a%20year%2C%20Gopal%20struggled%20to%20bring%20students%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F241073%2Fias-hero-arunachal-pradesh-civil-service-officers-pool-money-repair-school-project-37-crowdfunding-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eattend%20the%20school.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20more%20dropouts.%20So%20I%20decided%20to%20go%20out%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20mingle%20with%20the%20community%2C%20and%20talk%20to%20them%20about%20sending%20the%20kids%20to%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20was%20able%20to%20convince%20the%20parents%2C%20he%20realised%20the%20students%20would%20not%20like%20the%20conditions%20they%20were%20being%20taught%20in.%20%E2%80%9COf%20course%2C%20it%20would%20be%20boring%20to%20study%20in%20such%20a%20school.%20There%20was%20no%20water%20connection%20in%20the%20school%2C%20and%20the%20walls%20were%20dark%20and%20boring.%20There%20was%20nothing%20in%20the%20school%20to%20attract%20the%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWanting%20to%20bring%20improvements%20to%20the%20school%2C%20he%20looked%20for%20funds.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20knew%2C%20there%20were%20funds%20allocated%20to%20bring%20such%20improvements%2C%20the%20bureaucracy%20of%20it%20all%20would%20take%20too%20much%20time.%20So%20I%20decided%20to%20invest%20my%20own%20money%20to%20make%20the%20school%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOf%20wall%20paintings%20and%20a%20library%20of%20magic%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20when%20the%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20Gopal%20found%20the%20perfect%20opportunity%20to%20make%20use%20of%20his%20free%20time.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20to%20plant%20saplings%20all%20around%20the%20school%20so%20that%20it%20blooms%20into%20a%20garden%20when%20it%20is%20time%20for%20students%20to%20come%20back.%20Since%20there%20was%20no%20water%20connection%20in%20the%20school%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20buy%20a%20tanker%20of%20water%20to%20maintain%20the%20garden%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tanker%20would%20cost%20about%20Rs%20300%20and%20would%20last%20for%20a%20week.%20Calling%20himself%20an%20%E2%80%9Cartist%E2%80%9D%20of%20sorts%2C%20he%20says%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20fun%20with%20the%20walls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20walls%20were%20mundane%20and%20not%20fit%20for%20a%20school.%20I%20wanted%20to%20paint%20animals%2C%20birds%2C%20murals%20and%20whatnot%20on%20them.%20I%20undertook%20the%20task%20of%20making%20the%20place%20the%20most%20colourful%20building%20in%20the%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20entering%20the%20school%20now%2C%20one%20is%20no%20longer%20greeted%20by%20a%20shabby-looking%20building%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20as%20if%20a%20rainbow%20itself%20has%20splashed%20colours%20onto%20the%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGopal%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20cleaned%20up%20the%20surroundings%20of%20the%20school%20and%20adorned%20the%20walls%2C%20and%20even%20the%20ceilings%2C%20with%20colourful%20paints%2C%20creating%20images%20and%20inscribing%20inspirational%20messages.%20The%20outcome%20was%20a%20cheerful%2C%20radiant%2C%20and%20lively%20environment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fschool-9-1708436883.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gopal%20also%20set%20up%20a%20new%20library%20in%20the%20school.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fschool-9-1708436883.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fschool-9-1708